messages.message: Hey guys, I put together a document to start discussing possible custom metric implementations. I know some of you may have some great ideas for this, so I gave edit permissions to anyone in Instabase, and you should feel free to add to the doc! https://docs.google.com/document/d/1U2mfcY27vvgBVPc5anBATIm8PWsaMXhQSivsAhoGkso/edit?usp=sharing
